                div.form-group
                    label Title (Optional)
                    input.form-control(type='text' value='A hipster argument' placeholder='Scene title')
                div.form-group
                    label Body
                    textarea.form-control
                        p "Food truck semiotics jean shorts asymmetrical, craft beer 3 wolf moon Kickstarter mixtape. Occupy Tumblr cardigan synth street art skateboard. Thundercats sriracha +1, High Life fashion axe mumblecore Schlitz. Vinyl small batch 8-bit bespoke, Wes Anderson Vice cred Banksy actually.
