                        p "Disrupt pork belly put a bird on it PBR&B, Godard master cleanse American Apparel viral retro forage quinoa taxidermy flexitarian semiotics. Schlitz selfies banjo slow-carb, art party selvage post-ironic Neutra Marfa synth Banksy meggings. Sartorial gluten-free wolf, biodiesel food truck yr Marfa skateboard Intelligentsia stumptown deep v Helvetica letterpress paleo you probably haven't heard of them. Single-origin coffee brunch banh mi, trust fund mustache flexitarian bespoke.
                        p "Cold-pressed flannel Marfa, four dollar toast retro locavore cliche Intelligentsia iPhone vegan mustache kitsch health goth. Gentrify Neutra selvage, sartorial fashion axe bicycle rights literally American Apparel meditation chillwave twee Vice health goth fingerstache brunch. Sriracha health goth before they sold out cronut, viral slow-carb lo-fi tattooed."
                        p
                            strong What do you say in response?
                h2 Choices
                h3 Choice 1
                div.well.well-sm
                    div.form-group.form-group-sm
                        p
                            label Display text
                            input.form-control(type='text' value='"Ugh."' placeholder='Display text')
